snippet.title: Depp’s wife Amber Heard in dog doo after sneaking dogs into Australia
snippet.description:
This morning we took our weekly trip across the Ditch.

Johnny Depp's wife has been summoned to appear in court across the Tasman, after illegally bringing the couple's pet dogs into the country.

Australian correspondent Jason Morrison joined Paul this morning.
"Amber Heard brought the dogs into Australia and they have decided to prosecute her, not Johnny Depp or the pilot, because she filled out the form and said she didn’t have any livestock or living animals on her."

Watch the full interview with Jason Morrison.
